## 9. Publicação de Carrossel — Meta Graph API

Fluxo confirmado (API v25.0):

```
1. POST /{ig-user-id}/media
   ?image_url={URL_SLIDE_1}&is_carousel_item=true
   → { id: "CONTAINER_1" }

2. Repetir para cada slide (máx 10, mín 2)

3. POST /{ig-user-id}/media
   ?media_type=CAROUSEL
   &children=CONTAINER_1,CONTAINER_2,...
   &caption={LEGENDA}
   → { id: "CAROUSEL_CONTAINER" }

4. POST /{ig-user-id}/media_publish
   ?creation_id=CAROUSEL_CONTAINER
   → { id: "IG_MEDIA_ID" }
```

**Specs:** JPEG recomendado, máx 8MB/slide, formato 4:5 (1080x1350px), até 2.200 chars no caption, até 30 hashtags.

